::Prowl/Annihilator::

Prowl sighs as Iron Raptor leans slightly away. He looks into her eyes for a 
moment before smiling. "If you wish." He say mockingly.

Prowl lands softly, setting Iron Raptor down. He kisses her again, excitement 
and love mixing in his head.

"Now where were we?" He asks, leaning slightly back, his hands pressing her 
to him.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Annihilator looks up at the scanners as they report two maximal signatures 
landing nearby. He growls. Time for some fun.

"Poisonbite, Killer, follow me, we have some maximals to fry..." He says as 
he walks out of the base, gun ready.
